short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Copies session data from one tab to another

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This plugin allows you to copy all session data from one tab to another in your browser. This makes it easy to test local applications against session data form a production environment.
